  "text": "Researchers have suggested that the young people (i.e., younger than 29 years old) represent a segment more susceptible to gambling problems than adults [CITATION_1] . Additionally, over the last decade, they have become the older adults [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
